INT ID(isdigit) LPAREN CHAR ID(ch) RPAREN
LBRACE
RETURN ID(ch) GE CT_CHAR(0) AND ID(ch) LE CT_CHAR(9) SEMICOLON
RBRACE

VOID ID(main) LPAREN RPAREN
LBRACE
CHAR ID(c) SEMICOLON
ID(put_s) LPAREN CT_STRING("c=") RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(c) ASSIGN ID(get_c) LPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
ID(put_i) LPAREN ID(isdigit) LPAREN ID(c) RPAREN RPAREN SEMICOLON
RBRACE
